Description:
~~~~~~~~~~~~

Action-packed death racing, this is what Speed Kills
is about!

Traditional, isometric, powered by Unreal Engine.

Players compete in various championships, ranging from bootleg
rallies on the outskirts of the galaxy to big-league
circuits set against the goliath skylines of metropolis
cityscapes. You can purchase offensive and defensive vehicle
 upgrades, buy new cars, collect power-ups and earn bonuses.


FEATURES
  Classic gameplay, inspired by the 16-bit isometric racing games
  5 planets/championships to compete
  Over 50 unique tracks
  8 fully customizable and upgradable vehicles, ranging from
  beefed-up pickup trucks to futuristic hovercars

Install:
~~~~~~~

Unrar, mount/burn, install the game, copy crack, and play
